model.name: Coletti2020 - QSP model of prostate cancer immunotherapy

body.pre:
This model is based on the publication: Coletti R, Leonardelli L, Parolo S, Marchetti L. A QSP model of prostate cancer immunotherapy to identify effective combination therapies. Sci Rep. 2020 Jun 3;10(1):9063. doi: 10.1038/s41598-020-65590-0
Comment: Eq. 3 - no listed species "R", therefore based on Eq. 1 and 2, R_2 used instead. Eq. 12 - no listed parameter "a_Df" in Table S1, a_Dc used based on parameter description.
Curation Comment: Simulations are not reproducing manuscript plots. Matlab code is available (Supplementary File 2 of the manuscript publication) but has not been tested, so would be worth reattempting model curation.
